<!-- ══════ FAQ ══════ -->
<section class="faq-section">
  <div class="eyebrow"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span><span class="eyebrow-text">Common Questions</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-title">FREQUENTLY<br>ASKED<br>QUESTIONS.</h2>
  <div class="gold-rule"></div>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">How much does flooring installation cost in Halifax?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Flooring costs vary by material, room size, and subfloor prep. Vinyl plank is typically the most affordable option; hardwood and large-format tile run higher. We provide free, itemized quotes — most projects range from a few hundred dollars for a single room to several thousand for a full home.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">How long does flooring installation take?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">A single room usually takes one day. A full main floor or multi-room project typically takes two to four days, depending on subfloor conditions, material, and complexity. We'll give you a realistic timeline before starting.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Do you supply the flooring materials or do I need to buy them?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">Either works. We can source materials through our trusted suppliers, or you can supply your own. If you've already purchased a specific product, just let us know and we'll work with what you have.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">Can you install new flooring over existing floors?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">In some cases, yes — it depends on subfloor condition, height differences at transitions, and flooring type. We always assess the existing surface first and give you an honest recommendation before any work begins.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-q">What areas in HRM do you serve for flooring?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
      <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner">We serve all of Halifax Regional Municipality — Halifax, Dartmouth, Bedford, Sackville, Cole Harbour, Fall River, Eastern Passage, Timberlea, Hammonds Plains, Tantallon, Waverley, Enfield, Elmsdale, Porters Lake, and surrounding communities.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

